ID: americanism
TITLE: Americanism

===

The pride of foregone bros
Who died in bloodshed or war
To which we lie, freedom me
Don't worry 'bout when you're gonna die
Soon 'nuff you'll be putting down the sky
Fight for your freedom and your pride
That Americanism

I am American born
For this my freedom is sworn
No one can take that away from me

No commie punk will take me down
Beat his ass hard deep into the ground
Won't stop 'til the world can hear the sound
Of Americanism
